                                            <tr style="height: 554px;">
                                                <td valign="top" align="center" width="310" id="Cell1756">
                                                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><img id="Picture2071" height="517" width="229" src="../assets/images/jikokuten-dhratarastra-plain-wood-50.3cm-asuka-era-7thC-horyuji.jpg" vspace="0" hspace="0" align="top" border="0" alt="Jikokuten (Shitenno)" title="Jikokuten (Shitenno)"><br>Jikokuten (Dhratarastra), Plain wood, 50.3 cm<br><a style="font-size: 8pt;" href="../html/asuka-art.html">Asuka Era</a>, 7th Century, Hōryūji Temple 法隆寺, Nara</span></p>
                                                </td>
                                                <td valign="top" align="center" width="310" id="Cell1757">
                                                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><img id="Picture2072" height="528" width="212" src="../assets/images/jikokuten-dhrtarastra-93cm-wood-with-pigments-heian-11-12thC-horyuji.jpg" vspace="0" hspace="0" align="top" border="0" alt="Jikokuten (Shitenno)" title="Jikokuten (Shitenno)"><br>Jikokuten (Dhrtarastra), 93 cm, Wood with Pigments<br><a style="font-size: 8pt;" href="../html/busshi-buddha-sculptors-heian-era-japan.html">Heian Era</a>, 11-12th century, Hōryūji Temple 法隆寺, Nara</span></p>
