                                                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0px;"><img id="Picture2139" height="763" width="200" src="../assets/images/jikokuten-Dhrtarastra-tang-dynasty-dunhuang-painting-JKT-page.jpg" vspace="2" hspace="0" align="top" border="0" alt="Jikokuten (Skt. Dhrtarastra), Tang Dynasty, Dunhuang, China, 9th Century Painting" title="Jikokuten (Skt. Dhrtarastra), Tang Dynasty, Dunhuang, China, 9th Century Painting" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0,0,0);"><br><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Jikokuten (East)<br>Chinese = C = Chíguó Tiān<br>Tang Dynasty, Ninth Century<br>H = 72 cm, W = 17 cm<br>Ink and colors on silk.<br>Palais du Louvre in Paris<br>No. EO.1172a<br>Paintings from the Hidden<br>Library Cave, Dunhuang, China.<br><br>Scanned from<br>&#8220;DUNHUANG: A Centennial <br>Commemoration of the Discovery<br>of the Cave Library.&#8221;<br>ISBN 7-5054-0716-3/J-0396.<br>First published in 2000<br>by Morning Glory Publishers,<br>Beijing, China</span></p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
